  "body": "**Description:**\r\n`NodeTree`, part of the `pkg/scheduler/internal/cache` is exporting a `NumNodes` field which allows to modify its value externally. This also means that this field is not thread-safe.\r\n\r\n**Solution:**\r\nExpose a method that returns this value in a thread-safe way and do not export the field.\r\n\r\n/kind bug\r\n/sig scheduling",
